{"meta":{"title":"3 Néfi 30","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/30?lang=por","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ//2013-06-222-3-nephi-30-64k-por.mp3","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"72c26484c6ca5c60938582dbf57b8deb28916065","data-aid":"124147295","data-aid-version":"2","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/30","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"por","data-orig-id":"bb2b74eb6a2d2ae50f45b51e5fb078b84c3b0b41","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"3 Néfi 30","description":"Ordena-se aos gentios dos últimos dias que se arrependam, venham a Cristo e sejam contados com a casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"3 Néfi 30","description":"Ordena-se aos gentios dos últimos dias que se arrependam, venham a Cristo e sejam contados com a casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"542\"></span>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124147422\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 30</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124147423\" id=\"study_summary1\">Ordena-se aos gentios dos últimos dias que se arrependam, venham a Cristo e sejam contados com a casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124147425\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Ouvi, ó gentios, e escutai as palavras de Jesus Cristo, o Filho do Deus vivo, as quais ele me <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>ordenou</a> que dissesse a respeito de vós, porque eis que ele me ordenou que escrevesse, dizendo:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124147426\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Afastai-vos todos, ó <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>gentios</a>, de vossos caminhos iníquos; e <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>arrependei-vos</a> de vossas maldades, de vossas mentiras e embustes; e de vossas libertinagens e de vossas abominações secretas e vossas idolatrias; e de vossos homicídios e vossas artimanhas sacerdotais e vossas invejas; e de vossas discórdias e de todas as vossas iniquidades e abominações; e vinde a mim e sede batizados em meu nome, a fim de que recebais a remissão de vossos pecados e recebais o Espírito Santo, para que sejais <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>contados</a> com o meu povo, que é da casa de Israel.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"30\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124147428\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=por#p12\">3 Né. 5:12–13</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124147430\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Gentios</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124147431\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Arrepender-se, Arrependimento</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note2c\" data-full-marker=\"2c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124147432\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27-29?lang=por#p27\">Gál. 3:27–29</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18-19?lang=por#p18\">2 Né. 10:18–19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.10-13?lang=por#p10\">3 Né. 16:10–13</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.22-25?lang=por#p22\">21:22–25</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10?lang=por#p10\">Abr. 2:10</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124147425","context":"ordenou","text":"<p data-aid=\"124147428\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=por#p12\">3 Né. 5:12–13</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=por#p12","text":"3 Né. 5:12–13"}]},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124147426","context":"gentios","text":"<p data-aid=\"124147430\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Gentios</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=por","text":"GEE Gentios"}]},"note2b":{"id":"note2b","marker":"2b","pid":"124147426","context":"arrependei-vos","text":"<p data-aid=\"124147431\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Arrepender-se, Arrependimento</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=por","text":"GEE Arrepender-se, Arrependimento"}]},"note2c":{"id":"note2c","marker":"2c","pid":"124147426","context":"contados","text":"<p data-aid=\"124147432\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27-29?lang=por#p27\">Gál. 3:27–29</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18-19?lang=por#p18\">2 Né. 10:18–1